Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, liblua50-dev, liblualib50-dev
Description: tolua++
 tolua++ is an extended version of tolua, a tool to integrate C/C++ code with
 Lua. tolua++ includes new features oriented to c++.
